review:
Super authentic food, lots of veggie options and great Service;

Thanks to Min and to the Team

Alexandra und Wolfgang from Bavaria

Angsana Lang Co has Rice Bar and Rice Bowl, which are right on top of each other. Rice Bar offers Japanese cuisine and Rice Bowl Asian cuisine from several regions of Asia, such as Thailand, Cambodia and of course Vietnam (o;

We stayed at Rice Bar and ate delicious sushi and a rice dish.
Super delicious! If you like, you can sit right at the bar and watch the sushi masters do their craft. Rice Bar is very stylishly decorated. A nimble and very accommodating Service have rounded off the great impression.
